ont-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Theirs is a vision =
of the future I want to see exist: one in which more people are creators, i=
n which people create, share, and remix in conversation with each other. Ce=
rtainly, one in which AI doesn&#8217;t replace artists, just gives them sup=
erpowers, the kind of world people say they want in some indefinite way but=
 that Dancho &amp; Jos&#233; have a definite opinion on how to bring about.=
&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height:=
 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Personally, there&#8217;s this barbell of compa=
nies I want to see exist in the world.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, =
55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>On =
the one side are the </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/ac6389=
32-80c2-4528-95e3-4a70daec8084?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjml=
XXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoratio=
n: underline;">Vertical Integrators</a><span>, the companies building big, =
difficult things in the physical world to create the conditions for abundan=
ce, prosperity, and freedom, companies that help humanity live longer and r=
icher. I write a lot about those.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54=
, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">On the =
other side are companies that make all of that living more fulfilling. The =
ones that answer the question: if we really do build machines that let us w=
ork less, what are we going to do with ourselves?&#160;</p><p style=3D"colo=
r: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;=
">There&#8217;s a lot of work between now and that future, hours after hour=
s spent sweating the details, getting the product just right for a small gr=
oup of artists who will tell other artists who will spread the word to the =
world.&#160;From Elsewhere to everywhere.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55,=
 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The art they=
&#8217;re making is unfinished &#8211; it might always be unfinished &#8211=
; but what [untitled] is belting at the top of its lungs is that there&#821=
7;s a lot of value in the process.&#160;</p><div style=3D"font-size: 16px; =
